  <description><![CDATA[<h2><span data-contrast="auto">Begin your Norwegian adventure in the town of Voss, which has a reputation for extreme sports, activities and epic views. Next, journey to Flam or Aurland where you’ll stay on the stunning shores of the Aurlandsfjord. Finally, round off your journey in the wonderful waterside city of Bergen.</span></h2>
<p>Discover the best of the Norwegian fjords on this iconic multi-centre holiday. It'll give you a taste of three different fjord towns in <a data-udi="umb://document/286d71b6bae94f84a7ac63448c015f54" href="/{localLink:umb://document/286d71b6bae94f84a7ac63448c015f54}" title="Norway" data-anchor="#">Norway</a> and the culture, activities and epic views on offer.</p>
<h3>Guide price from: £1,632pp*</h3>
<p><strong>Your multi-centre holiday options:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>This multi-centre is a minimum of nine nights with a choice of durations in your chosen hotels</li>
<li><span data-contrast="auto">Any day arrivals</span></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Your holiday includes:  </strong><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}"> </span></p>
<ul>
<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="2" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;multilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">Return flights from the UK</span></li>
<li>Return airport transfers (direct) to and from your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Transfers between your chosen destinations</li>
<li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="2" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;multilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><span data-contrast="auto">Ferry from Flam or Aurland to Bergen through the Sognefjord</span></li>
</ul>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to Book Your Multi-Centre Holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your multi-centre holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? Consider it done. Dial in and let our experts plan your dream getaway. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><em>*Prices are based on 2 people sharing for 3 nights in a Twin Standard Railway Room at Fleischer's Hotel, Voss, 3 nights in a Twin Room with Fjord Views at Heimly Guesthouse, Flam, and 3 nights in a Twin Room at Thon Hotel Bristol Bergen, Bergen, with train/ferry transfers between resorts, departing on the 1st of June 25 from London Gatwick airport. Supplements for alternative flights, flight routes, and room types may apply. Prices are correct at the time of publishing on 21/11/24 but are subject to change based on availability. Please call for the most up-to-date pricing and availability before booking.</em></p>]]></description>
