  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Recommended Hotels in Flam &amp; Aurland</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/557f2a4f36ec40ea8e5a3c74fa16141c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/557f2a4f36ec40ea8e5a3c74fa16141c}" title="Hotel Aurlandsfjord" data-anchor="#">Hotel Aurlandsfjord</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13107862/hotel_aurlandsfjord_flam___aurland_bedroom_copyright_-norwaysbest-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Aurlandsfjord, Aurland" data-udi="umb://media/af5bbf6823c840eab01e74cf4c5efc06" /></p>
<p>The Hotel Aurlandsfjord is in a great location in the village of Aurland, that sits on the shores of one of the Sognefjords branches. You’re around 20 minutes by bus from Flam here so you have the best of both worlds, a peaceful base with access to Flam.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/b908838c0d1246a1aa1194e2525cca65" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b908838c0d1246a1aa1194e2525cca65}" title="Fretheim Hotel" data-anchor="#">Fretheim Hotel</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13107847/fretheim_hotel_flam___aurland_exterior_copyright_-norwaysbest-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Fretheim Hotel, Flam" data-udi="umb://media/ff12b74046be4694a1787cf344f359fa" /></p>
<p>The Fretheim Hotel is one of the original hotels in the village of Flam. It’s got a long history and makes a great stopping point for those wanting to explore more of the Sognefjord and nearby areas.</p>
<p><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px;" src="/media/13107847/fretheim_hotel_flam___aurland_exterior_copyright_-norwaysbest-1.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="Fretheim Hotel, Flam" data-udi="umb://media/ff12b74046be4694a1787cf344f359fa" /></p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/18b94b9d5f4d4510a6c23eecf8a70de1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/18b94b9d5f4d4510a6c23eecf8a70de1}" title="Flam &amp; Aurland" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">View all Hotels in Flam &amp; Aurland</a></p>]]></facilityDescription>
  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<h2>Recommended Hotels in Voss &amp; Bergen</h2>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/d3f5962b236745d08320581985566eef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d3f5962b236745d08320581985566eef}" title="Thon Hotel Orion" data-anchor="#">Thon Hotel Orion, Bergen</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13108106/thon-hotel-orion_lounge-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Thon Hotel Orion, Bergen" data-udi="umb://media/a24d7a55854b40f7afb2b4655276ca65" /></p>
<p>With a fantastic position in the heart of Bergen’s historic centre you can easily explore the city centre, or, get into the mountains and explore the walking trails. Come back to a comfortable, cosy base.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/dadc1503a43d4cd79064b98f92c3f7f9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dadc1503a43d4cd79064b98f92c3f7f9}" title="Thon Hotel Bristol Bergen" data-anchor="#">Thon Hotel Bristol, Bergen</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13108091/thon-hotel-bristol-bergen-standard-room-twin-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Thon Hotel Bristol, Bergen" data-udi="umb://media/d820125e77ab43aa9a5dfcf10ec64840" /></p>
<p>The Thon Hotel Bristol in Bergen makes a great choice for anyone wanting a central location- with many of Bergen's most popular sights right on your doorstep.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/63fdf14c11cc4e13bb9c80029763bf09" href="/{localLink:umb://document/63fdf14c11cc4e13bb9c80029763bf09}" title="Fleischers Hotel" data-anchor="#">Fleischers Hotel, Voss</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13107921/fleischers_hotel_voss_hotel_exterior-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Fleischers Hotel, Voss" data-udi="umb://media/b86c0ffbddc04bd6bf111905ae082e1e" /></p>
<p>The Fleischers Hotel in Voss offers a fantastic lakeside location and is just across from the local train station. With its grand building and traditional décor as well as great facilities including and indoor swimming pool, it makes for a comfortable stay.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/c79f1cba7d6c4332bc4418e75ca6f72d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c79f1cba7d6c4332bc4418e75ca6f72d}" title="Park Hotel" data-anchor="#">Park Hotel, Voss</a></h3>
<p>Set in its own beautiful lakeside grounds close to the town centre, the impressive Park Hotel enjoys a deserved reputation for its friendly service, superb wine cellar and elegant Elysee restaurant. The piano bar and lakeview lounges are comfortable and cosy places to relax.</p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/3bff04d1881648b5a6163cdd11cfb562" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3bff04d1881648b5a6163cdd11cfb562}" title="Voss" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">View all Hotels in Voss</a></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5}" title="Bergen" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">View all Hotels in Bergen</a></p>]]></familyDescription>
