  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Experience the best of the Norwegian Fjords on our Best of Norway multi-centre holiday. From extreme sports and epic views in Voss, to relaxing on the shores of the Aurlandsfjord in Flam or Aurland and rounding off your trip in the cultural haven of Bergen.</p>]]></listingDescription>
  <listingImage><![CDATA[umb://media/8ff33f0f044340629a16e9416eccf222]]></listingImage>
  <localFees></localFees>
  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p><span class="TextRun SCXW65779519 BCX8" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW65779519 BCX8">A multi-centre holiday lets you mix and match hotels, lengths of stay, and exciting activities to create your ideal trip. Enjoy </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW65779519 BCX8">plenty of activities and day trips on offer in Voss</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW65779519 BCX8"> whilst nature and scenery are the main attractions in Flam and </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW65779519 BCX8">Aurland</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW65779519 BCX8"> which sit on the shores of the </span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW65779519 BCX8">Aurlandsfjord</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW65779519 BCX8">. Finally, rounding off your trip in the historic town of Bergen.</span></span></p>
<p><strong>Begin your adventure in Voss</strong></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">Voss sits sandwiched between two lakes and is great for those wanting to have plenty of options of things to do in the area. Embark on some of the walking trails around Voss or you’ll find water sports on the lakes during certain months of the year. The centre of the town has several shops and cafe’s to wander in to. Or, buy yourself some tickets to the Voss gondola for fantastic scenery and plenty of walking.</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/3bff04d1881648b5a6163cdd11cfb562" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3bff04d1881648b5a6163cdd11cfb562}" title="Voss" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">Find Out More About Voss</a></p>
<p><strong>Unforgettable views</strong><strong> in Flam or Aurland</strong></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">Flam and Aurland are both villages that are just 20 minutes apart by bus and from Voss you can get there by train. They both offer fantastic scenery and a position on the Aurlandsfjord, which is one of the branches of the Sognefjord. It’s up to you which village you’d like to stay in. Flam is famous for the Flam railway which leaves from Flam and heads to Myrdal. The railway brings in a lot of day trippers as it’s a must-see destination in Norway. Aurland on the other hand, is a little more peaceful and not as well connected, but has incredible fjord views. For things to do, you’ll find plenty of walking, cycling and viewpoints, so make sure you get out and see this natural paradise.</span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/18b94b9d5f4d4510a6c23eecf8a70de1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/18b94b9d5f4d4510a6c23eecf8a70de1}" title="Flam &amp; Aurland" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">Find Out More About Flam &amp; Aurland</a></p>
<p><strong>The waterside city of Bergen </strong></p>
<p><span data-contrast="auto">Bergen is a beautiful city and it's not just about the destination but the journey to get here. From Flam or Aurland to Bergen you’ll catch the ferry– it's a long trip, around five and a half hours, but the scenery is spectacular. As you cruise down the Sognefjord you’ll gaze in awe at the one of Norway’s largest fjords. Once in Bergen you can make the most of those city sights. Head to the old town and see the colourful houses of Bryggen Wharf or get yourself a ticket and head up in the funicular to Mount Floyen for plenty of picturesque walking trails. There are seven mountains surrounding Bergen, so you won’t be short on walking routes.</span><span data-ccp-props="{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}"> </span></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d517b2c21fa94eb096a3bcb6b7e933c5}" title="Bergen" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center" data-anchor="#">Find Out More About Bergen</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></locationDescription>
